description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Another world under the sea
-Pond with waterfall
-House in a colorful garden
-A forest where animals play and the sea where yachts sail
-The city of Paris full of flowers
-Beautiful garden on the lake
-Forest of Animals
-Quiet and large waterfall
-Beach with dancing dolphins
-Beautiful Asian Gardens
name: Spectrum Sceneries: The Digital Canvas
